Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.750 --> 00:00:02.020
Yodingizda bo‘lsin, XML yaratayotganda,

00:00:02.020 --> 00:00:04.480
joylashuv tartibini yaratishga yordam 
beradigan uchta qadam mavjud.

00:00:05.540 --> 00:00:07.950
Birinchi qadam - ko‘rinishlarni tanlash.

00:00:07.950 --> 00:00:10.045
Bu yerda siz qanday ko‘rinishlardan 
foydalanishni va qancha 

00:00:10.045 --> 00:00:10.796
foydalanishni o‘ylab ko‘rasiz.

00:00:11.910 --> 00:00:15.700
Rejalashtirishingizga yordam berish 
uchun aytaman, siz foydalanmoqchi 

00:00:15.700 --> 00:00:16.910
bo‘lganingiz nechta TextViews, ImageViews va 
tugmachalar ekanligini bilishingiz kerak.

00:00:17.970 --> 00:00:20.320
Agar siz ushbu ko‘rinishlardan birini ishlatmasangiz, 
unda davom eting 

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:20.830
va bu yerga nol yozing.

00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:25.270
Keyingi, ikkinchi bosqich - bu ko‘rinishni 
joylashtirish, va agar esingizda bo‘lsa, 

00:00:25.270 --> 00:00:27.530
bunda ko‘rinish guruhlari bilan shug‘ullanish kerak.

00:00:27.530 --> 00:00:29.930
Siz ushbu joylashuv tartibi uchun qaysi 
guruhdan foydalanmoqchisiz va 

00:00:29.930 --> 00:00:31.610
nima uchun bu guruhni tanlaganingizni 
aytishingizni istayman.

00:00:31.610 --> 00:00:34.420
Maslahat, haqiqatan ham biz ikkita ko‘rinish 
guruhlari haqida bilib oldik, 

00:00:34.420 --> 00:00:36.510
shuning uchun ularning qaysi biri 
ekanligini tanlash juda oson bo‘lsa kerak.

00:00:37.530 --> 00:00:40.490
Va nihoyat, uchinchi bosqich - bu ko‘rinishlarni tartibga solish.

00:00:40.490 --> 00:00:43.230
Va bu yerda matn rangi kabilarni o‘zgartirish 
uchun qanday atributlardan 

00:00:43.230 --> 00:00:45.020
foydalanishingiz haqida o‘ylang.

00:00:45.020 --> 00:00:48.160
Va, albatta, bu yerda e’tibor berishingizni 
istagan xususiyatlar bu ilovani 

00:00:48.160 --> 00:00:50.062
o‘qishga yordam beradigan xususiyatlardir.

00:00:50.062 --> 00:00:52.300
Biz buni yakuniy bosqichga chiqarmoqdamiz.

00:00:52.300 --> 00:00:54.010
Shunday qilib, margin va padding kabi narsalar haqida o‘ylang.

00:00:55.100 --> 00:00:57.500
Ko‘rinishlarni tekislash va 
markazlashtirishga yordam beradigan 

00:00:57.500 --> 00:01:00.240
ikkita foydali atribut: joylashuv tartibi 
va tortishish kuchi mavjud.

00:01:01.300 --> 00:01:04.200
Men ushbu ikki atribut haqida ko‘proq 
ma’lumot olishingiz uchun o‘qituvchining 

00:01:04.200 --> 00:01:06.290
yo‘riqnomalarida ularga havola berdim.

00:01:07.470 --> 00:01:09.620
Va nihoyat, bajarib bo‘lgandan so‘ng, 
oldinga o‘ting 

00:01:09.620 --> 00:01:11.860
va ushbu katakchaga bosing.

00:01:11.860 --> 00:01:14.370
Agar ilova nimaga o‘xshashligini unutgan 
bo‘lsangiz, u mana shunga o‘xshashligini eslatmoqdaman.

00:01:14.370 --> 00:01:16.640
Ushbu savollarga javob berishda yordam bo‘lishi 
uchun ushbu rasmdan foydalaning.

